<br>
However, this is not a LDON spell, it's a quest spell from LOY.<br>
<br>
Anyway, it acts like a mana dot on casters mobs without breaking mez...plus it gives that mana to you.  The spell gives you 50 mana per tick for one minute, whether or not the caster mob dies before the one minute is up.<br>
<br>
Wish it had a shorter recast time, but even with the long recast time, I still find myself keeping this spell ready pretty often in ldon groups.<br>
<br>
--Maob, 65 Enchanter on Luclin<br>
